name: THE FASHION FIRM X SEED LETTERMAN JACKET

metadata.name: THE FASHION FIRM X SEED LETTERMAN JACKET 1/20
metadata.description:
Founded by designer Dante Beals, The Fashion Firm has created custom pieces for Future, Snoop Dogg, and many more. Beals has also collaborated with brands such as Gatorade.
For the Seed The Blockchain exhibition, The Fashion Firm is collaborating with SEED to drop its first ever NFT-The Fashion Firm x SEED Letterman Jacket. To celebrate SEED's grand opening, Beals designed a custom collection of one-of-one letterman jackets featuring SEED's aesthetic and references to nature. Only twenty unique pieces will be available.
Collectors must purchase the NFT in order to receive the physical jacket. Upon purchasing they will be fitted for their size. Holders of the NFT will also receive exclusive access to future collaborations between SEED and The Fashion Firm, as well as become part of the SEED NFT ecosystem.
